transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Good morning sir.
Customer: Haan, good morning.
Executive: Haan sir keh raha hu ki kab free hai thoda ek bar bata dijiye main catalog designing ke liye bhejunga.
Customer: Kya baat hua tha apna?
Executive: Catalog designing ke liye bhejna hai na to ek bar mujhe bata dijiye product aap monday ko call karne wale the.
Customer: Monday ko na?
Executive: Haan.
Executive: Sir monday ko lagaya tha main ek second shayad laga nahi tha.
Executive: Maine monday good morning bhi bola tha sir aur ek bar call kiya tha shayad morning me hi disconnect ho gaya tha.
Executive: Mujhe laga aapne call nahi aaya call.
Customer: Achcha.
Executive: Sir aaj possible hai?
Customer: Kya karna hai?
Executive: Video meet pe aa jaiye main karwa de raha hu ek bar proper bata dijiye jyada time nahi lunga matra 10 minute lunga.
Customer: Kya karna kya hai boliye na.
Executive: A ispe product aap mujhe bata dijiye konse highlight karane hai.
Executive: Thik hai aur jispe konse product ko jyada target karna hai.
Executive: Hot selling product jo jyada rahega jispe aap jyada focus karenge sir.
Customer: Haan to jo product usme dale hue hai.
Executive: Haan haan sir dale me se hi.
Customer: Haan to unme se hi kar de na.
Executive: Haan haan wahi sir main dekho ye keh raha hu ki thoda sa product ke naam proper kara lijiye.
Customer: Lifting tools and tackles.
Executive: Haan haan ek minute rukiye bata raha hu.
Executive: Aap uspe system ke samne hai sir?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Ek minute.
Executive: Dekhiye praveen.rajbhar@indiamart se aaya hoga.
Executive: Ye wali email id hai sir aapki.
Executive: Sir mail aaya hoga mere side se.
Customer: Kya karna hai usko?
Executive: Join kijiye please.
Customer: Upar wala ya niche wala?
Executive: Nahi ask to join karke aa raha hoga na google meet pe click karenge to.
Customer: Achcha.
Customer: Join upar wala haan.
Executive: Kiya? Main hi karunga share aapko.
Executive: Kar diya aapne?
Customer: Yes, admit kar raha hu.
Executive: Main screen share kar raha hu thik hai na sir?
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Thoda sa mujhe apna bata dijiye ki kaise kaise rahega ye base pe main taki aapko better kam karke de paye.
Executive: Sir screen dikh rahi hai hamari?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Haan sir dekhiye aapka na jo India mart pe jo catalog hai jisme ki aapne ye product dala hua hai hydro testing service right?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Thoda sa product ka naam aap correctly bataiye jayega ek hydro testing service hai ek cylinder hydro testing service hai.
Customer: Nahi cylinder wala nahi karna hai pressure vessel hydro testing services.
Executive: Ek second.
Executive: Haan jaise hydro testing service rakhna hai na?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Aur kaunsa bol rahe hai ki nahi rakhna hai?
Customer: Usme cylinder likha hai na hum cylinder ka testing nahi karte hum pressure vessel aur storage tank ka karte hai.
Executive: Achcha to ye cylinder hydro testing hata du product haan haan.
Executive: Isko na main deactivate kar de raha hu abhi aapko kahan se delete karna hoga bata deta hu aur sir aur isme dekhiye 34 product aapke catalog me active hai thik na?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: To isme jaise sir product ka naam main confirm kar raha hu bas bata dijiye mujhe jaise sir lifting tools and tackles inspection service hai ye sahi hai?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Aur uske baad haan ye product dekhna sir explosive license consultant service.
Customer: Haan sahi hai.
Executive: Thik hai category iski jo map hai explosive license ka haan ya ye kar sakte hai?
Customer: Nahi.
Customer: Ye kya hai alternate name license consultant ye chalega na licensing services chalega.
Executive: Nahi pata nahi kya hai.
Customer: Hello.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants catalog designing.

- Wants to remove cylinder hydro testing service.

- Wants to confirm product names in catalog.



Resolution:

- Executive offered a video meet to discuss catalog.

- Executive deactivated cylinder hydro testing service.

- Executive confirmed product names with customer.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- catalog, product, services, designing
